{"tid":124731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TRUMP開鍘！無證華裔、韓裔恐掃地出美","createTime":"2017-02-18T00:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T06:11:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bba146af783d705782fd4bf2898ac136307d12","tid":124731,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/川普開鍘-無證華裔-韓裔恐掃地出美-201600831.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%96%8B%E9%8D%98-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94-%E9%9F%93%E8%A3%94%E6%81%90%E6%8E%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E-201600831.html&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3a495d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/川普開鍘-無證華裔-韓裔恐掃地出美-201600831.html</a><br />\n<br />\n川普開鍘！無證華裔、韓裔恐掃地出美<br />\n作者三立新聞網 | 三立新聞網 <a href=\"http://setn.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsetn.com&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=837c187e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsetn.com&h=93013817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">setn.com</a> &ndash; 2017年2月15日 上午4:16<br />\n<br />\n記者李慧蘋／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n川普上任後備受爭議的移民法，在全美大規模逮捕無證居留的非法移民，雖然當局聲稱其中95%都是罪犯，但民間風傳移民局鎖定紐約、洛杉磯等華人最多的城市，已經逮捕40人，讓當地華人人心惶惶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/77134afcb6266a5a198a7740f6687774\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F77134afcb6266a5a198a7740f6687774&h=6f93b8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自SBS<br />\n<br />\n韓國大學生：「我很擔心，我就是被驅逐的人之一，就算回南韓，以我家的狀況恐怕也活不下去。」<br />\n<br />\n華人圈人心惶惶，而向來雇用外籍勞工的成衣工廠，也面臨員工被抓光的窘境。洛杉磯成衣廠韓裔老闆：「如果真的強制遣返，我們成衣廠的生意一定被重創。我有心理準備隨時倒閉，因為找不到人上班。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/620033e1de21e63261320ea0746e1d31\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F620033e1de21e63261320ea0746e1d31&h=f0bd5e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自SBS<br />\n<br />\n紐約舉行千人遊行示威，但冰天雪地中看不到華人身影，就怕露面身分曝光面臨遣返命運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/438ba5d24d5dda3d45d9496c920e7b09\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F438ba5d24d5dda3d45d9496c920e7b09&h=fc6fda1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abb3196245e88b05a62fd63d007689647b4d6919","tid":124731,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/b0e281bdeae46df41842124948e32213\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fb0e281bdeae46df41842124948e32213&h=508bf9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自abc NEWS<br />\n<br />\n總統川普推特發文，強調是「兌現競選承諾」，打擊非法移民等於剷除都市的毒瘤。白宮資深政策顧問米勒：「這麼做不但能拯救國人性命，還能顧全國人的權益。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/60621dc02ad875c6407fed9a7a673428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F60621dc02ad875c6407fed9a7a673428&h=44ad87a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自abc NEWS<br />\n<br />\n身為一連串爭議命令的幕後推手，白宮資深顧問米勒罕見現身，但發言跟川普一樣脫稿演出。白宮資深政策顧問米勒：「無論何時，美國總統的言行都是百分之百正確的。」<br />\n<br />\n強勢作風、發言另人咋舌，在川普上任後鐵腕治國，讓曾是充滿美國夢的自由疆土蒙上陰影。"},{"pid":"344552c23f47b2dbcef0138db4917c924d9016f6","tid":124731,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcfc7a7aff07ca277a920f45399a9178040861e","tid":124731,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"咁你係無証呀"},{"pid":"5435dfd234c7ca99a40898f4e0a17a295aadd6