住唔駛講，食餐cheap cheap中式自助餐任食都係6-8蚊，其他垃圾食唔就更唔在講。但非法中國人時薪都有5蚊以上，做按摩等特種行業都1k5起跳，未計tips。<br />\n<br />\n基本餐飲行業係缺人嘅。全美國有1200萬人做餐飲業，當中極大多數係非法移民。<br />\nobama時期唔係唔捉，係從來冇主動捉，歸管由移民局負責，但一直人手不足。但當非法移民犯事被警察捉到後都巡例會做下嘢，主要邊防移民局做把關。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有friend在LA做country 執法人員。"},{"pid":"2295ccf0e570038c565ba22b557b719eecf2e03d","tid":124731,"uid":5151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"又用華人代表中國人"},{"pid":"2ad10edae6c60da991f5ba8f586e385daf43904b","tid":124731,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時黎哂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港寧願要呢批好過要蝗"},{"pid":"d11c0801d246c319757b3d3adbed7fee28b72e3b","tid":124731,"uid":43133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa6ebe6895c9438d7bd57b07e9652d55aa5dcd0","tid":124731,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87e139283331fc3f72ca14798b5d9ddeb2224d6","tid":124731,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無證仲可以打工？</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑工</blockquote><br />\n澳洲大把 身邊就有個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請黑工唔拉僱主？"},{"pid":"4d52ebe1bfd7b8898cf00ff469d3a79f5090bf0a","tid":124731,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"無証黑工緊係要掃走啦"},{"pid":"c61c5d6b4ffb5b3a21f87df0a282df7d704190db","tid":124731,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04